text: An excellent bus stop. Profesionally constructed with sturdy seats and comfortable weather protection. Lots of busses coming at regular intervals, and there are a lot of amenities in the vicinity. Highly recommended for all bus stop enthusiasts.
This is the place back in the 70 and 80 where cinema show along East coast road for Roxy,palace and Odeon Katong theatre head the entertainment.
Air condition, good varieties of choices for food
Conveniently in front of Moda & Katong V!!

Various merchants in this square include catering, clothing, tailoring, furniture, beauty salons, nail art, and traditional Chinese massage. Photocopying, jewelry store, food store, daily necessities store, Chinese mathematics education center and car trading center. Without the demolition of the overpass and the impact of the epidemic, it would be difficult to find a store here. Parking lots, escalators, and elevators with visibility are accessible and convenient.
